  "instructions": [
    "Combine carrots and beets in a pressure cooker and cook for 10 minutes.",
    "Let the pressure cooker cool, then chop the carrots and beets into smaller pieces.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the chopped carrots, beets, cucumber, radishes, onion, and garlic.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together apple cider vinegar and olive oil. Pour the dressing over the vegetables and toss to combine.",
    "Sprinkle salt and black pepper over the salad and toss again to combine.",
    "Cover the bowl with plastic wrap and refrigerate for at least 30 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "Serve the salad chilled, garnished with chopped fresh herbs if desired."
